Available options for godi.conf:

- GODI_LABLGTK2_USE_GL: wether to attempt building openGL support.
  Requires both LablGL and GtkGLarea.
  Example: GODI_LABLGTK2_USE_GL=yes

- GODI_LABLGTK2_CONFARGS: other options for configure.
    --without-glade          disable glade support
    --without-rsvg           disable SVG support
    --without-gnomecanvas    disable gnomecanvas support
    --without-gnomeui        disable gnome druid support
    --without-panel          disable gnome panel support
    --enable-debug           compile with debug info
